quran[10{c,v,t}:
11,72,"woh boli"" haae meri kam bakhti! kya ab mere haan aulaad hogi jabkay mein budiya phons ho gayi aur yeh mere miyan bhi boorhay ho chuke? yeh to barri ajeeb baat hai """
11,73,"firshton ne kaha"" Allah ke hukum par taajjub karti ho? ibrahim ke ghar walo, tum logon par to Allah ki rehmat aur uss ki barkaten hain, aur yaqeenan Allah nihayat qabil tareef aur barri shaan wala hai """
11,74,phir jab ibrahim ki ghabrahat daur ho gayi aur ( aulaad ki basharat se ) is ka dil khush ho gaya to is ne qoum Loot ke muamlay mein hum se jhagra shuru kya
11,75,haqeeqat mein ibrahim bara Haleem aur naram dil aadmi tha aur har haal mein hamari taraf rujoo karta tha
11,76,"( aakhir-kaar hamaray firshton ne is se kaha )"" ae ibrahim, is se baz aa jao, tumahray rab ka hukum ho chuka hai aur ab un logon par woh azaab aakar rahay ga jo kisi ke phairay nahi phir sakta """
11,77,aur jab hamaray farishtay loot ke paas puhanche to unn ki aamad se woh bohat ghabraya aur dil tang howa aur kehnay laga ke aaj barri museebat ka din hai
11,78,"( un mehmanon ka aana tha ke ) is ki qoum ke log be ikhtiyar is ke ghar ki taraf daud parre pehlay se woh aisi hi bad karyon ke khogar thay loot ne un se kaha"" bhayyo, yeh meri betiyan mojood hain, yeh tumahray liye pakeeza tar hain kuch khuda ka khauf karo aur mere mehmanon ke muamlay mein mujhe zaleel nah karo kya tum mein koi bhala aadmi nahi? """
11,79,"unhon ne jawab diya"" tujhe to maloom hi hai ke teri baityon mein hamara koi hissa nahi hai aur to yeh bhi jaanta hai ke hum chahtay kya hain """
11,80,"loot ne kaha"" kash mere paas itni taaqat hoti ke tumhe seedha kar deta, ya koi mazboot sahara hi hota ke is ki panah laita """
11,81,"tab firshton ne is se kaha ke"" ae loot, hum tairay rab ke beje hue farishtay hain, yeh log tera kuch nah bigaar saken ge bas to kuch raat rahay apne ahal o Ayal ko le kar nikal ja aur dekho, tum mein se koi shakhs peechay palat kar nah dekhe magar teer y biwi ( sath nahi jaye gi ) kyunkay is par bhi wohi kuch guzarnay wala hai jo inn logon par guzarna hai un ki tabahi ke liye subah ka waqt muqarrar hai subah hotay ab der hi kitni hai! """
